<item>
            <title>[SHINDIG-1480] Return the converted error code rather than the one from ResponseItem</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SHINDIG-1480</link>
                <project id="12310741" key="SHINDIG">Shindig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The DataServiceServlet#sendError check for possible error code for JSON-RPC case and try to convert it as much as it can.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However when actually setting the error code to HttpServletResponse it uses the one from ResponseItem instead of the &quot;converted one&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12492879">SHINDIG-1480</key>
